div.div: Nageki no Bourei wa Intai Shitai

Six childhood friends make a vow one day to become treasure hunters, and eventually grow to be the strongest heroes in the world. During his first quest, Krai Andrey realizes he isnt cut out for the job. Even so, his friends make him their leader. Underpowered in the face of great expectations, Krai embarks on a reluctant heros tale of glory, headaches, and wanting to retire early.
(Source: Crunchyroll)
Akuyaku Reijou Level 99: Watashi wa Ura Boss desu ga Maou de wa Arimasen

This college kid wants nothing more than a quiet life. So when shes reborn as Yumiella, the hidden villainess of an Otome RPG, shes not exactly thrilled. Still yearning for peace, she abandons her evil duties to live a more discreet life. Until her gamer side kicks in and she accidentally reaches level 99! Now, everyone suspects that shes the infamous Demon Lord. What future awaits her?
(Source: Crunchyroll)

Duke Kallen de Lewelton is bloodthirsty and ruthless when it comes to killing criminals, but a total sucker when it comes to his new daughter! Peasant girl Lae learns this herself when a fateful run-in with the duke results in her adoption into the Lewelton home. Armed with a sharp mind and the knowledge from her past life, Lae makes the perfect addition to the familys quest to quell injustice. But as the mysteries of the capitals underbelly rise to the surface, will she and her new family withstand the return of a true criminal mastermind?
(Source: Tapas)
Comedy, Drama, Romance, Slice of Life

When Ayumi learns that her senior Yuuki is heading to Minami High School, a fairly difficult institution to enroll in, she believes her current results are insufficient to pass the entrance exam. Despite this, he gives her a word of encouragement and promises to tutor her if she succeeds.
One year passes, and Yuuki finds Ayumi to be one of the new first-year students enrolling at his school. However, he also quickly realizes that his junior has become extremely flirtatious toward him! Now fulfilling his promise, the two experience many events togetherwhether they be funny, embarrassing, or even romantic.
